Build Identifier: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; WOW64; rv:2.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/4.0

Allow having mixed pb and non-pb tabs opened at the same time. Pages opened manually would inherit the current pb mode the browser is in. Pages opened by following links or by javascript would inherit the pb mode of the parent page.

This would then also allow fancy things like per-domain pb and so on.

Reproducible: Always</thetext>
